AWSTemplateFormatVersion: '2010-09-09'

                    NodeGroup:
                        Value: !Ref NodeGroup

                        Properties:
                          DesiredCapacity: 2
                          LaunchConfigurationName: example-aws-profile-role-nodeLaunchConfiguration-0f23611
                          MinSize: 1
                          MaxSize: 2
                          VPCZoneIdentifier: ["subnet-0408073b4e012218d","subnet-0acfcd89e77586427","subnet-0405889d4b4e72a64"]
                          Tags:
                          
                          - Key: Name
                            Value: example-aws-profile-role-eksCluster-7da9528-worker
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                          - Key: kubernetes.io/cluster/example-aws-profile-role-eksCluster-7da9528
                            Value: owned
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                        UpdatePolicy:
                          AutoScalingRollingUpdate:
                            MinInstancesInService: '1'
                            MaxBatchSize: '1'
